title: Hard.Enduro.2013.Tough.One.FUEL.720P.h264.English
description:
We look forward to some of the roughest, toughest races of the year including The Tough One, Hell's Gate, Erzberg Rodeo, Red Bull Romaniacs and Red Bull Sea to Sky. Featuring Graham Jarvis, Jonny Walker, Dougie Lampkin and a host of top riders.

Living up to it's fearsome reputation, the Tough One at the Nantmawr Quarry in Shropshire, England put the world's best extreme riders through their paces on a course that was littered with rocks, logs, mud and even snow.
